00:22:57.350 --> 00:22:58.720
Turning a blind eye to problems,

00:22:58.720 --> 00:23:00.240
that's how life goes by.

00:23:00.480 --> 00:23:01.920
We're women.

00:23:03.880 --> 00:23:04.790
Sis,

00:23:06.350 --> 00:23:07.590
I know that.

00:23:08.570 --> 00:23:10.280
What on earth happened?

00:23:10.520 --> 00:23:11.670
What's going on?

00:23:12.000 --> 00:23:12.830
What schoolgirl?

00:23:12.830 --> 00:23:13.350
Mom,

00:23:14.680 --> 00:23:16.210
you don't need to know that.

00:23:17.000 --> 00:23:20.530
You just have to know that
Siyun understands what's important,

00:23:20.750 --> 00:23:22.150
and she's my dear sister.

00:23:25.350 --> 00:23:26.830
Young Master,

00:23:26.830 --> 00:23:28.630
Mr. Qiao is waiting in the study.

00:23:30.790 --> 00:23:31.350
Good.

00:23:32.590 --> 00:23:33.160
Be good.

00:23:34.210 --> 00:23:35.230
You're the best.

00:23:44.400 --> 00:23:44.990
Jinghan.

00:23:46.070 --> 00:23:47.470
You don't need to pull me.

00:23:47.650 --> 00:23:48.780
I can walk by myself.

00:23:51.590 --> 00:23:53.450
You're really my sweetie sister.

00:24:01.310 --> 00:24:03.040
Here comes my brother-in-law!

00:24:04.790 --> 00:24:06.640
Look how well Siyun is doing.

00:24:07.550 --> 00:24:08.640
And you

00:24:08.790 --> 00:24:10.250
look quite spirited, too.

00:24:12.160 --> 00:24:14.160
