00:29:07.830 --> 00:29:08.690
In my business,

00:29:08.720 --> 00:29:10.890
different times bring different cases.

00:29:10.890 --> 00:29:12.240
I'm just doing my small business,

00:29:12.240 --> 00:29:14.000
focusing on my own job.

00:29:14.510 --> 00:29:16.110
Political affairs

00:29:16.750 --> 00:29:18.030
are too grand for me.

00:29:18.400 --> 00:29:20.330
Only outstanding persons like you

00:29:20.510 --> 00:29:21.910
can handle such matters.

00:29:25.780 --> 00:29:26.650
Actually,

00:29:26.680 --> 00:29:27.930
if you work for me,

00:29:27.960 --> 00:29:30.720
you just change your work environment.

00:29:31.070 --> 00:29:32.940
But the clients you serve
would be different.

00:29:32.940 --> 00:29:33.800
Think about it.

00:29:34.020 --> 00:29:34.700
Who do you

00:29:34.920 --> 00:29:36.480
serve every day here?

00:29:36.750 --> 00:29:37.480
Tom,

00:29:37.750 --> 00:29:38.610
Dick and Harry,

00:29:38.830 --> 00:29:39.440
right?

00:29:39.720 --> 00:29:40.720
In my department,

00:29:40.720 --> 00:29:42.070
we serve the country.

00:29:42.510 --> 00:29:43.860
The strategic vision and elevated thinking

00:29:43.860 --> 00:29:45.060
will be worlds apart.

00:29:45.080 --> 00:29:46.000
Let me ask you something.

00:29:46.000 --> 00:29:46.640
