and Senior Mrs. Zhu,

00:36:15.510 --> 00:36:16.960
let me say something

00:36:16.960 --> 00:36:17.890
as a modest spur.

00:36:19.360 --> 00:36:21.090
Today is truly a wonderful day,

00:36:21.440 --> 00:36:22.710
a joyous occasion.

00:36:23.510 --> 00:36:24.840
My daughter Yi

00:36:25.150 --> 00:36:27.030
is well-educated.

00:36:27.230 --> 00:36:28.920
