00:36:44.320 --> 00:36:45.400
The Zhu family

00:36:45.880 --> 00:36:47.150
values

00:36:48.320 --> 00:36:50.230
being benevolent, righteous,
courteous, wise, and trustworthy.

00:36:50.230 --> 00:36:53.070
Most importantly,
their financial situation is quite good,

00:36:53.070 --> 00:36:53.760
isn't it, Senior Mrs. Zhu?

00:36:53.760 --> 00:36:55.510
