00:38:42.320 --> 00:38:43.070
Dare you defy me?

00:38:43.070 --> 00:38:44.070
Dare you do it again?

00:38:44.070 --> 00:38:44.920
Get up there.

00:38:44.920 --> 00:38:45.580
Kneel down!

